Gluster 3.2: Using NFS to Mount Volumes[ Using NFS to Mount Volumes>>]

This section describes how to use NFS to mount Gluster volumes (both
manually and automatically) and how to verify that the volume has been
mounted successfully.

*Note:* NFS does not work with CTDB and NLM due to absence of locking
support.

